Invicta 52mm Russian Diver Nautilus Swiss Mechanical Leather Strap Watch gold tone dial The very definition of bold design, this Invicta Russian Diver makes an undoubted impression! Beginning with a round stainless steel case, this Russian Diver perfectly suits your smart style. Housing a silver-tone coin edged push/pull crown and a canteen style protector with a chain on the left side of the case, this timepiece keeps control in your hands. This timepiece features two wing-style function pushers and fixed bezel on the top. The case boasts cool details to keep you ahead of the curve and fit your personal taste. The cage-like top can be removed and the hinged case back can open to reveal a coveted Swiss Made ETA 6497 Mechanical movement. Fully accentuating your sharp style, a leather strap brings this Russian Diver together. The grey and black strap secures with a buckle etched with the Invicta logo and two matching strap keepers. “Invicta” and its logo share the space on the back of the strap with “Genuine Leather” for the final finishing details. A timepiece worthy of the spotlight, make this Russian Diver your newest Invicta purchase today!
